{"tid":1864643,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"全球危機 - 口罩荒 : 香港市民口罩夠唔夠頂一個月？","createTime":"2020-02-05T17:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T08:53:14.000Z","uid":163149,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e561edc778121ac3107396015f56cc5e9d3372e9","tid":1864643,"uid":163149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"全球都奶野， 泰國台灣限制口罩出口。 連挪威口罩都俾支那人掃哂， 日本自己都危危乎。<br />\n除非外國疫情好快控制住，如果唔係應該唔會有幾多口罩輸出到俾香港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以普通市民，我諗大家採購埋d 儲貨之後，各國之後都未必有貨輸出到。<br />\n<br />\n若果香港疫情一個月兩個月控制唔到， 市民又冇辦法買到口罩，應該有唔少人會放棄口罩到時交叉感染恐怕會黎多獲大爆發。<br />\n<br />\n封關真係刻不容緩，如果一兩個月控制唔到， 恐怕真係要全港停工匿係屋企"},{"pid":"3d4b2c3b1b119c8e630e658f57593d09373e4194","tid":1864643,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:07:30.000Z","msg":"根本公司無貨就咪叫人返工"},{"pid":"eec5bf238b2b4bb8824827542d7d38981bf8fa0b","tid":1864643,"uid":177168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:09:16.000Z","msg":"我在呢度呼籲巴士、地鐵、航空、入境、同海關工會在2月10日或之前盡快表決通過罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1864623\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1864623</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDPGeQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuDPGeQ.png&h=f227900c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家疫情有爆發跡象，十萬火急！藍田女手足全家確診武漢肺炎，請大家幫手簽下面的聯署：<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手行多步宣傳下比你ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同身邊既朋友。<br />\n另外大家亦可以透過聯署同twitter自行遊說美方人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呼籲研發出肺炎解藥的美國藥廠供貨香港救手足救香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=19b88cbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-supply-remdesivir-drug-w